WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:05.520
Well, good evening family. Thank you for

00:00:03.280 --> 00:00:08.000
joining us again tonight. We're going to

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:10.639
go over some of the news today and what

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.200
happened in the last two days—all the

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:15.518
things that are happening in the news.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:19.600
President Trump has been very

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:21.600
busy. We

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:25.199
have a lot to pray about, and I'm

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:27.359
annoyed about the Clarity

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:31.119
Act and things that Braden was telling

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:33.200
me. Our senators are a

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:36.320
blessing, especially the

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:38.960
Democratic ones. Will you fix that

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:40.719
fan for me, buddy?

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:42.640
No, just turn it up because it's

00:00:40.719 --> 00:00:44.640
blowing in my face.

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:48.160
I bumped it; it was my fault.

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:50.719
Angle it up

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:54.480
so it just circulates above me, because

00:00:53.199 --> 00:00:56.800
I don't like it blowing straight in my

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:58.000
face.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:04.080
Braden said, 'Did you know

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:06.960
that we have to have seven Democrats

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:10.320
flip and vote with us for the Clarity Act?'I

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:12.798
didn't know

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:15.600
we had to have that many. We

00:01:12.799 --> 00:01:17.680
have to have seven for that.

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:19.360
I was saying, well, hopefully Fetterman, who is

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:22.320
in

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:24.960
Pennsylvania, will vote Republican,

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:28.559
but that means all Republicans have to

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:31.199
vote this way.

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:33.439
We have to have six more Democrats, and

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:36.799
three of them are throwing a fit because

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:39.919
President Trump made $2 billion

00:01:36.799 --> 00:01:43.491
in 2025 and it came out. They

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:45.920
want to put an amendment

00:01:43.491 --> 00:01:48.880
to the bill,

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:51.040
from what I understand, that his kids

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:53.360
can't make any money off of the Clarity

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:55.280
Act.

00:01:55.280 --> 00:02:01.439
They were upset

00:01:56.880 --> 00:02:03.199
he made $2 billion.

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:05.439
I'm not going to be negative; I'm

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:08.560
going to say, 'Wow.'It's

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:09.840
just annoying to me. What do

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:13.360
his kids have to do

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:16.080
with it? I just try

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:17.599
to stay neutral on this and

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:20.879
pray because I know what the Lord has

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:23.280
told me—that we must pray for

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:27.200
the

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:29.360
Clarity Act to pass.

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:33.518
Politics are politics.

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:38.319
Japan

00:02:33.519 --> 00:02:42.319
passed their

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:45.280
own Clarity Act

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:46.319
today.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:51.119
It's going to

00:02:48.959 --> 00:02:53.920
take a fuller effect in 2027.

00:02:53.920 --> 00:03:00.720
The Lord said, 'Watch the Sooners,'which

00:02:57.360 --> 00:03:04.560
was Japan, South Korea, and

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:08.159
the Asian nations.

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:12.159
He said they would be first before

00:03:08.159 --> 00:03:14.879
America, and just like the Lord said, it's

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:15.760
happening.

00:03:16.159 --> 00:03:20.720
Japan has their stuff together. They

00:03:18.239 --> 00:03:22.159
know what's coming and

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:23.599
want to be ahead of it.

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:27.839
The Sooners were the

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:30.000
ones that took the land before the land

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:32.239
run in Oklahoma. I saw the boomer

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:34.879
schooner wagon going across the land.

00:03:32.239 --> 00:03:38.239
The Lord said Japan and the

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:42.079
Sooners will be first—I mean

00:03:38.239 --> 00:03:45.840
South Korea.

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:47.519
Asia is going all in on crypto.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:52.000
President Trump warned that other

00:03:47.519 --> 00:03:54.799
nations could outpace the US on crypto

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:57.920
regulation. South Korea has now

00:03:54.799 --> 00:04:02.239
recognized crypto as a national asset

00:03:57.920 --> 00:04:03.839
and plans to tokenize state-owned real

00:04:02.239 --> 00:04:04.560
estate.

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:10.799
Meanwhile, Japan is paving the way for

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:13.200
crypto ETFs and lower taxes.

00:04:10.799 --> 00:04:15.439
So, they're trying to be the Sooners,

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:17.519
just like the Lord said. Isn't Jesus

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:19.680
wonderful that he would tell us

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:21.280
they would do that first?

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:23.440
He's trying to give us some

00:04:21.279 --> 00:04:25.359
encouragement when we have senators that

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:28.320
are dumb.

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:31.759
Japan officially

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:34.320
passes laws recognizing crypto as a

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:38.560
financial asset.

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:40.560
Just like the Lord said.

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:42.320
Isn't that interesting? I

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:44.639
think it's interesting whenever you hear

00:04:44.639 --> 00:04:50.639
a word over a year ago

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:51.759
and the Lord brings it to pass.

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:59.360
Braden

00:05:03.199 --> 00:05:06.240
translated

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:11.039
the

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:15.840
report from

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:18.080
the Committee

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:19.679
on Financial Affairs. This bill

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:21.758
aims to respond to changes in our

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:23.919
country's financial and capital markets,

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:25.840
expand the supply of growth capital, and

00:05:23.919 --> 00:05:27.758
ensure market fairness, transparency,

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:29.440
and investor protection by bringing

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:30.960
crypto asset transactions under the

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:33.199
regulation of financial instrument

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:35.520
transactions. It seeks to

00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:37.520
establish a public disclosure system for

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:39.359
information related to crypto assets,

00:05:37.520 --> 00:05:41.520
develop systems for the disclosure of

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:43.919
specific non-financial information and

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:45.520
audit certification,

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:49.039
and review

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:51.120
regulations on unfair trading.

00:05:53.280 --> 00:05:55.919
I think it's cool.

00:05:55.919 --> 00:06:00.320
I wonder if that's what his

00:05:57.520 --> 00:06:00.799
voice really sounds like.

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:10.639
It sounds very similar;

00:06:10.639 --> 00:06:13.039
it has that

00:06:11.919 --> 00:06:13.359
softness.

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:21.759
After the Lord spoke to us

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:24.800
about the Sooners, which

00:06:21.759 --> 00:06:27.120
would be South Korea and Japan, we saw

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:29.199
Taiwan jump on this.

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:34.400
The Lord warned us about

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:36.560
the Asians. He said that the Asians

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:39.280
will ride the wave first and then

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:42.319
America will ride it after, but they

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:45.440
will be ahead in the finances of

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:47.039
investing first. There

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:50.080
will be

00:06:47.039 --> 00:06:51.840
a lot of crypto-billionaire Asians in my

00:06:50.080 --> 00:06:54.719
opinion.

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:08.720
On July 11th, the Lord

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:11.199
gave us a word about a pipeline

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:13.360
coming out of the Kurds.

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:17.280
He said there will

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:19.840
be oil deals in the days ahead for

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:23.599
Iraq. I saw Iraq come up out of

00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:26.318
nothing—Rolls-Royces,

00:07:23.599 --> 00:07:28.800
beautiful

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:30.880
homes, and palm trees.

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:33.759
The Lord said,

00:07:30.880 --> 00:07:36.479
'Corruption, corruption, corruption,'as

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:38.800
you'll hear. But I thought it

00:07:36.479 --> 00:07:41.360
was interesting that the Lord warned us

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:43.120
what was coming on July 11th.

00:07:53.840 --> 00:07:57.359
In the prayer,

00:07:57.360 --> 00:08:03.280
I see the pink currency again. I

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:06.240
see Iraq and

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:08.239
Babylon rising. I

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:18.319
see a new era

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:21.280
for Iraq around the

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:24.319
oil.

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:30.800
I

00:08:27.440 --> 00:08:33.838
see a rising of Iraq

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:37.120
as Iran crumbles

00:08:33.839 --> 00:08:40.719
and the Prince of Persia

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:42.240
is losing its

00:08:40.719 --> 00:08:45.440
grip.

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:49.279
Iran is losing its grip upon Iraq.

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:54.480
I see three faces in

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:56.800
Iraq. One has a

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:58.880
black mustache;

00:08:56.800 --> 00:09:01.439
he's heavier set with a five o'clock shadow. He looked like

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:06.399
Saddam

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:12.399
in his younger years.

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:20.399
Iraq will rise in the days ahead over

00:09:15.920 --> 00:09:23.199
the oil and a pipeline

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:26.080
with the Kurds.

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:32.800
When Iran is dealt with, it's Kuwait. I

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:34.480
see Iran in a stone age in some areas,

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:37.199
trying to get

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:39.839
other nations around there to step in

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:42.640
and help. Trying to get Turkey and Syria to help.

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:49.040
It's the

00:09:45.440 --> 00:09:51.200
art of the deal with the oil concerning

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:54.959
the Strait and

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:58.240
reestablishing a safer area

00:09:54.959 --> 00:10:01.199
for all of us, a denuclearization of

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:04.720
Iran. It's an art of the deal. Saudi Arabia—it's

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:05.440
alliances.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:10.800
And now we've got news coming in.

00:10:06.959 --> 00:10:12.880
Congressman, the US, Syria, and Iraq

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:15.920
are reportedly going to revive that

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:18.160
historic 500-mile pipeline to Syria's

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:19.760
Mediterranean coast, an oil pipeline to

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:21.680
bypass the Hormuz Strait. There are

00:10:19.760 --> 00:10:23.279
multiple pipelines ramping up to

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:25.519
circumvent Iran. What do you make of

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:27.439
this? We know that's a percentage of

00:10:25.519 --> 00:10:30.240
the overall delivery of oil through the

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:33.200
Strait, but it's ramping up now. Iraq

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:35.120
has tremendous potential because of

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:37.279
their oil.

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:38.959
We're

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:41.279
going to be doing a lot of deals. We're

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:42.560
going to create a lot of jobs for both

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:44.880
countries and take

00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:47.518
out a lot of oil. A lot of oil is coming

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:49.600
out, and American companies are

00:10:47.519 --> 00:10:50.720
doing it—mostly American companies now.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:54.640
They don't want to do business with

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:58.720
others. I say they will set Iran back

00:10:54.640 --> 00:11:00.800
even further into the Stone Age, for an

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:04.079
attack against their infrastructure is

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:08.640
coming, and it will be against their

00:11:04.079 --> 00:11:12.640
electric grid. I see an attack

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:16.000
setting them back

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:21.279
to the Stone Age—not all of it, but some of

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:23.839
it dead. Many

00:11:21.279 --> 00:11:27.519
are

00:11:23.839 --> 00:11:29.600
contemplating ground invasions

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:32.800
with troops on the ground, using

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:35.839
Saudi Arabia and Kuwait.

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:38.240
They're debating

00:11:35.839 --> 00:11:41.200
boots on the ground to go and finish

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:44.399
this off—battalions and

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:46.800
arming the civilians—though not swaying

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:50.480
so much that way. I see them

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:54.560
trying to cut the cord to the internet, the

00:11:50.480 --> 00:11:56.399
underwater cables concerning Iran.

00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:59.119
I hear them

00:11:56.399 --> 00:12:01.680
threatening to cut underwater cables in

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:03.600
Iran. It's about the

00:12:01.680 --> 00:12:05.439
internet. They don't have the stuff to

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:06.959
do it; it's a lot of threats. They don't

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:10.720
have the stuff to do

00:12:06.959 --> 00:12:13.040
it; it's too deep.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:16.000
You know the

00:12:13.040 --> 00:12:18.399
word kamikaze? It's to the point

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:20.399
of that desperation;

00:12:18.399 --> 00:12:24.000
they're

00:12:20.399 --> 00:12:27.440
hitting a desperation point.

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:29.120
This is a very scary point.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:32.560
I see them doing something

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:36.720
desperate to try to—it's about

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:39.199
bringing forth a Mahdi. "We must do this,"they say.

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:41.200
I see them trying to strike.

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:48.240
They have Israel in their sights. Do you

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:49.680
know when you look through some glasses?

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:53.279
I see it like one of

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:54.959
those little things that has a

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:56.320
spin wheel on it—the

00:12:54.959 --> 00:12:58.800
little thing you put on your

00:12:56.320 --> 00:13:01.600
face as a kid. They're looking in the

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:02.880
sights toward Israel,

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:04.720
but they're looking

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:06.240
towards Syria.

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:14.000
Concerning Israel, they

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:16.719
have a weapon. I told you, I saw it in

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:20.720
there: that black rocket.

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:25.839
They have one weapon; it's not been

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:30.480
tested. It's underneath

00:13:25.839 --> 00:13:33.200
that mountain. I see a weapon

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:34.959
underneath their mountain; it's hidden.

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:36.720
I see their leader;

00:13:34.959 --> 00:13:40.880
they're done. The man that's

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:43.040
leading now is going to be done. His

00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:45.200
days are numbered. After

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:47.439
another air strike,

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:50.240
he's done.

00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:59.440
Another regime change

00:13:57.040 --> 00:14:02.480
is coming. They don't want civil war in

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:04.160
the country

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:06.480
like in

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:11.199
Afghanistan.

00:14:06.480 --> 00:14:13.040
An unstable Iran is

00:14:11.199 --> 00:14:15.519
dangerous because of what they have

00:14:13.040 --> 00:14:18.639
underneath that mountain.

00:14:15.519 --> 00:14:20.560
An unstable Iran is

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:22.320
dangerous. They need a

00:14:20.560 --> 00:14:23.680
good government because some of

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:27.120
these people that are in leadership still

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:29.760
right now are crazy—a

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:31.920
proxy government. I pray over any troops

00:14:29.760 --> 00:14:34.720
on a ground invasion. I pray over our

00:14:31.920 --> 00:14:37.279
troops and our people. It's not

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:41.440
so much us; it's to assist the others around

00:14:37.279 --> 00:14:43.760
it. "Will you get involved with

00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:45.519
this?"It's

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:47.439
not our fault; it's not our problem.

00:14:45.519 --> 00:14:50.560
It's like, "We need you, Saudi

00:14:47.440 --> 00:14:53.760
Arabia and some of these other nations."It's

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:56.479
the art of the deal

00:14:53.760 --> 00:15:00.800
with Turkey and other

00:14:56.480 --> 00:15:03.279
nations. "Will you help us with

00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:04.719
this?"I

00:15:03.279 --> 00:15:07.199
don't know if this is what's being

00:15:04.720 --> 00:15:12.000
discussed, but I

00:15:07.199 --> 00:15:14.639
hear this: "Will you help us with this?"Because

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:15.920
NATO and these others are

00:15:14.639 --> 00:15:17.600
in La La

00:15:15.920 --> 00:15:19.120
Land.

00:15:17.600 --> 00:15:20.720
But I'm seeing them trying to bring up

00:15:19.120 --> 00:15:24.079
Jordan and these other nations

00:15:24.079 --> 00:15:30.399
to bring a stable Iran. An

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:33.600
unstable Iran is dangerous to the

00:15:30.399 --> 00:15:36.000
region. They're even trying to talk to Pakistan, but

00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:39.760
Pakistan doesn't want to be involved with freedom fighters—for

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:42.720
the kamikazes,

00:15:39.760 --> 00:15:47.839
the people

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:50.800
in their own land.

00:15:47.839 --> 00:15:54.079
That's interesting. Good job.

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:56.160
He cut out all the tongues so it just

00:15:54.079 --> 00:15:58.399
flowed without having to pray. I pray it,

00:15:56.160 --> 00:15:59.680
and then I see it, and he just cut it

00:15:58.399 --> 00:16:00.639
all out. That's why it kept

00:15:59.680 --> 00:16:02.239
editing, because

00:16:00.639 --> 00:16:04.639
he's cutting out tongues.

00:16:02.240 --> 00:16:08.079
Yeah,

00:16:04.639 --> 00:16:10.079
I like that. Sometimes it makes

