01:12:28.960 --> 01:12:34.560
the Lord. And if Jesus did it, I'm going

01:12:33.040 --> 01:12:36.640
to do it. If David did it, I just go,

01:12:34.560 --> 01:12:38.480
'Hey, man. He's just a man. I

01:12:36.640 --> 01:12:39.840
want to be like that.'Because God said he was a

01:12:38.480 --> 01:12:41.759
man after his own heart. So, I'm just

01:12:39.840 --> 01:12:43.440
like, 'Hey, if that's what you're

01:12:41.760 --> 01:12:45.040
looking for, a man that's quick to

01:12:43.440 --> 01:12:48.320
repent.'He

01:12:45.040 --> 01:12:50.400
was quick to repent.

01:12:48.320 --> 01:12:53.040
In the last days, we must be quick to

01:12:50.400 --> 01:12:54.719
repent. If we mess up, we run to the

01:12:53.040 --> 01:12:57.360
Father. We don't run from God when we

01:12:54.719 --> 01:12:59.520
sin. We run to God. 'Oh, Father, forgive

01:12:57.360 --> 01:13:01.360
me.'Because

01:12:59.520 --> 01:13:03.360
the Bible says that in the last

01:13:01.360 --> 01:13:04.880
days, men will be lovers of themselves.

01:13:03.360 --> 01:13:07.839
And people that are lovers of themselves are

01:13:04.880 --> 01:13:09.840
not quick to repent.

01:13:07.840 --> 01:13:13.520
It's about me,

01:13:09.840 --> 01:13:16.239
my, my. I want to be

01:13:13.520 --> 01:13:17.760
about him. So, I hope that helps

01:13:16.239 --> 01:13:19.280
you. People are saying, 'Well, what do we

01:13:17.760 --> 01:13:20.800
do when you got things

01:13:19.280 --> 01:13:22.320
bumping in the night?'Well, when you

01:13:20.800 --> 01:13:24.320
got things bumping in the night, you

01:13:22.320 --> 01:13:28.799
take the authority of the believer and

01:13:24.320 --> 01:13:30.799
you apply the blood of Jesus.

01:13:28.800 --> 01:13:33.800
Tell the devil, 'You get out of my

01:13:30.800 --> 01:13:33.800
house.'You

01:13:34.239 --> 01:13:39.839
don't have to be tormented by a

01:13:36.719 --> 01:13:42.400
demon. Demons are supposed to be

01:13:39.840 --> 01:13:43.920
tormented by you.

01:13:42.400 --> 01:13:45.280
They're

01:13:43.920 --> 01:13:46.719
supposed to—when you wake up every

01:13:45.280 --> 01:13:50.639
morning, they go, 'Oh my God,

01:13:46.719 --> 01:13:52.880
she's awake!'and they run.

01:13:50.640 --> 01:13:57.400
Submit yourself therefore unto God.

01:13:52.880 --> 01:13:57.400
Resist the devil and he will flee.

01:13:58.159 --> 01:14:03.120
I'm not going to allow a pig to be

01:13:59.920 --> 01:14:04.640
inside of me. If they

01:14:03.120 --> 01:14:06.400
cast them out and put them in pigs—Jesus

01:14:04.640 --> 01:14:08.239
put them in a pig—I'm not going to allow

01:14:06.400 --> 01:14:10.480
something that should be in a pig inside of me.

01:14:08.239 --> 01:14:12.879
No, no, no. I'm not going to

01:14:10.480 --> 01:14:15.759
allow you to torment me.

01:14:12.880 --> 01:14:18.239
I am covered by the

01:14:15.760 --> 01:14:20.560
blood of Jesus. And that's another thing

01:14:18.239 --> 01:14:22.480
people get upset and say, 'Well, you

01:14:20.560 --> 01:14:24.640
can't be possessed with the devil,

01:14:22.480 --> 01:14:26.400
Brandon, because you're a born-again Christian.'Never

01:14:24.640 --> 01:14:27.679
said you could.

01:14:26.400 --> 01:14:29.360
There's a difference between being

01:14:27.679 --> 01:14:32.360
possessed with the devil and being

01:14:29.360 --> 01:14:32.360
oppressed.

01:14:33.360 --> 01:14:39.519
Big difference.

01:14:36.239 --> 01:14:42.159
And I have seen it both ways. Tongue-talking,

01:14:39.520 --> 01:14:43.840
Holy Ghost-filled people oppressed

01:14:42.159 --> 01:14:47.120
by stuff because they open the door to

01:14:43.840 --> 01:14:49.440
it. You're looking at porn and you're

01:14:47.120 --> 01:14:52.159
talking in tongues on Sunday? The devil

01:14:49.440 --> 01:14:53.599
will get a foothold in you.

01:14:52.159 --> 01:14:54.960
You're looking at porn, you're doing

01:14:53.600 --> 01:14:56.320
things you shouldn't be doing. You know

01:14:54.960 --> 01:14:57.840
you're not supposed to be doing it.

01:14:56.320 --> 01:15:00.159
You're opening the door to a devil and

01:14:57.840 --> 01:15:01.679
they'll oppress you.

01:15:00.159 --> 01:15:03.920
They'll get a hold of your mind, get a

01:15:01.679 --> 01:15:06.000
stronghold on your mind. Yes, they will.

01:15:03.920 --> 01:15:07.440
If you're inviting the devil in, he'll—'Well,

01:15:06.000 --> 01:15:09.520
you know what? We're just going to

01:15:07.440 --> 01:15:12.320
do social drinking on the weekends and

01:15:09.520 --> 01:15:14.480
we just get a little buzzed. We get a

01:15:12.320 --> 01:15:16.559
little tipsy. We don't get totally

01:15:14.480 --> 01:15:18.559
wasted, but we get a little buzzed.'You're

01:15:16.560 --> 01:15:20.800
opening the door to the devil.

01:15:18.560 --> 01:15:22.080
He'll come right in on

01:15:20.800 --> 01:15:23.920
you and you'll start dealing with

01:15:22.080 --> 01:15:25.840
alcohol all the time. 'Well, I have to

01:15:23.920 --> 01:15:28.159
have a whole bottle,'then two

01:15:25.840 --> 01:15:32.920
bottles, now three bottles, 'but I'm

01:15:28.159 --> 01:15:32.920
not an alcoholic. I'm not an alcoholic.'You

01:15:33.760 --> 01:15:39.800
give the devil just a little bit of

01:15:35.679 --> 01:15:39.800
room and he'll take a mile.

01:15:40.000 --> 01:15:44.640
Same thing with all kinds of

01:15:42.080 --> 01:15:45.679
stuff, y'all. We all have

01:15:44.640 --> 01:15:49.679
something we're going through,

01:15:45.679 --> 01:15:51.840
right? But we apply the blood. I'm

01:15:49.679 --> 01:15:54.640
just trying to help,

01:15:51.840 --> 01:15:56.640
telling you how to be free.

01:15:54.640 --> 01:15:58.960
The word of God will keep you

01:15:56.640 --> 01:16:01.040
free and set you free. But you've got to

01:15:58.960 --> 01:16:02.800
know the truth, and the truth of God's

01:16:01.040 --> 01:16:03.840
Word will set you free. I'm trying

01:16:02.800 --> 01:16:05.840
to tell you, there's a lot of people

01:16:03.840 --> 01:16:08.000
walking around with a lot of baggage and they

01:16:05.840 --> 01:16:09.520
don't even realize it.

01:16:08.000 --> 01:16:12.400
People don't teach

01:16:09.520 --> 01:16:16.239
that stuff at church anymore,

01:16:12.400 --> 01:16:18.239
especially about the demonic.

01:16:16.239 --> 01:16:20.320
And I've seen people they want to admit

01:16:18.239 --> 01:16:21.440
them into insane asylums and they go,

01:16:20.320 --> 01:16:22.960
'Well, we've got to put them on medication.'No,

01:16:21.440 --> 01:16:26.320
they've got a

01:16:22.960 --> 01:16:28.080
devil they need to be free of.

01:16:26.320 --> 01:16:30.239
There's a lot of people who have some stuff

01:16:28.080 --> 01:16:32.320
attached to them. They've got attachments,

01:16:30.239 --> 01:16:33.919
is what I call them. And I'll walk

01:16:32.320 --> 01:16:36.080
around and listen, and with the gift that

01:16:33.920 --> 01:16:37.760
I walk in, I'll walk around and say,

01:16:36.080 --> 01:16:39.040
'That one right there has

01:16:37.760 --> 01:16:40.560
something they need. It's on their shoulder.'And

01:16:39.040 --> 01:16:42.560
a lot of times it looks

01:16:40.560 --> 01:16:43.840
like a monkey. They'll be attached on

01:16:42.560 --> 01:16:46.000
their shoulder, and they'll have a band

01:16:43.840 --> 01:16:49.120
around their head. I'll see all these

01:16:46.000 --> 01:16:51.760
attachments. Is it inside of them, like

01:16:49.120 --> 01:16:53.760
in their spirit? No, the Holy

01:16:51.760 --> 01:16:56.719
Ghost is there. But you allow

01:16:53.760 --> 01:17:04.520
baggage to be like a snot

01:16:56.719 --> 01:17:04.520
rag. It tries to latch onto you;

01:17:04.800 --> 01:17:10.719
it tries to sit on your

01:17:06.800 --> 01:17:12.239
shoulder, and you allow it. But I'm

01:17:10.719 --> 01:17:13.440
Holy Ghost; I'm wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

01:17:12.239 --> 01:17:16.159
He's not inside of me; he's just an

01:17:13.440 --> 01:17:19.199
attachment on the outside.

01:17:16.159 --> 01:17:21.120
Does that make sense? I am wall-to-wall

01:17:19.199 --> 01:17:23.199
Holy Ghost.

01:17:21.120 --> 01:17:26.679
But you allow little attachments

01:17:23.199 --> 01:17:26.678
on your shoulder.

01:17:29.520 --> 01:17:33.120
Can they stay? No, not if you get in the

01:17:31.600 --> 01:17:36.080
Word.

01:17:33.120 --> 01:17:38.400
Not if you shut the doors to stuff and

01:17:36.080 --> 01:17:41.360
you don't allow him in. But

01:17:38.400 --> 01:17:44.080
he goes from here to here, and the

01:17:41.360 --> 01:17:45.679
next thing you know, you've opened it up

01:17:44.080 --> 01:17:48.800
and now he's grabbing hold of

01:17:45.679 --> 01:17:51.040
your head. I've seen people

01:17:48.800 --> 01:17:52.400
walk around with stuff on their head and

01:17:51.040 --> 01:17:54.640
they're

01:17:52.400 --> 01:17:56.639
growling, acting a certain

01:17:54.640 --> 01:18:00.000
way, but they're praying in tongues, and

01:17:56.640 --> 01:18:01.360
I'm going, 'What gives with that?'They're

01:18:00.000 --> 01:18:02.960
baptized in the Holy Ghost;

01:18:01.360 --> 01:18:04.320
they're tongue-talkers.

01:18:02.960 --> 01:18:07.360
They know

01:18:04.320 --> 01:18:11.759
how to believe God for some stuff, but

01:18:07.360 --> 01:18:14.400
they've got stuff manifesting on them,

01:18:11.760 --> 01:18:16.880
and I've seen it all.

01:18:14.400 --> 01:18:20.639
And so you get mad, but Lester Sumrall will

01:18:16.880 --> 01:18:22.719
tell you the same thing.

01:18:20.640 --> 01:18:24.800
But it depends on what

01:18:22.719 --> 01:18:27.040
circles you get in. There are all kinds

01:18:24.800 --> 01:18:30.000
of different circles. I have to tell you

01:18:27.040 --> 01:18:32.719
that I was one that had eight,

01:18:30.000 --> 01:18:35.679
and my mom and dad had to get me some

01:18:32.719 --> 01:18:39.760
help. We went to certain places and

01:18:35.679 --> 01:18:42.960
they didn't believe it.

01:18:39.760 --> 01:18:46.719
They wanted to admit me and I was

01:18:42.960 --> 01:18:50.320
ready to kill myself. I had such a

01:18:46.719 --> 01:18:54.480
problem with depression and suicide,

01:18:50.320 --> 01:18:56.480
and it was terrible.

01:18:54.480 --> 01:18:58.639
They put me on

01:18:56.480 --> 01:19:02.000
medication and gave me these pills,

01:18:58.640 --> 01:19:03.600
and I was so sedated I'd run into walls

01:19:02.000 --> 01:19:05.040
because they thought, 'This guy's really

01:19:03.600 --> 01:19:07.760
messed up. We've got to get him some help.'So

01:19:05.040 --> 01:19:09.840
they put me on medication, and

01:19:07.760 --> 01:19:11.679
my mom and dad—when the guy said

01:19:09.840 --> 01:19:14.000
because I was so bad we could

01:19:11.679 --> 01:19:16.239
put him in the hospital—my

01:19:14.000 --> 01:19:18.560
dad went on a four-day

01:19:16.239 --> 01:19:21.599
fast (I believe it was more than

01:19:18.560 --> 01:19:23.440
that, a five-day fast) and started

01:19:21.600 --> 01:19:24.960
fasting

01:19:23.440 --> 01:19:26.559
because nobody at the church could help

01:19:24.960 --> 01:19:29.199
us.

01:19:26.560 --> 01:19:30.960
Nobody; they didn't believe it. 'Well,

01:19:29.199 --> 01:19:33.678
he's baptized in the Holy Ghost. What's

01:19:30.960 --> 01:19:36.320
going on with him?

01:19:33.679 --> 01:19:38.480
Well, he just needs counseling.'So

01:19:36.320 --> 01:19:40.960
we went to get counseling. And I was

01:19:38.480 --> 01:19:43.280
working for a big ministry, and they

01:19:40.960 --> 01:19:45.840
paid for it: 'We'll send him to this over here.'And

01:19:43.280 --> 01:19:47.840
here I am with my radio

01:19:45.840 --> 01:19:50.719
turning on in the middle of the night—turning

01:19:47.840 --> 01:19:52.480
on heavy metal,

01:19:50.719 --> 01:19:56.620
turning on stuff. Creepy

01:19:52.480 --> 01:19:58.639
stuff was going on; creepy stuff.

01:19:59.120 --> 01:20:04.880
I didn't know what to do,

01:20:01.679 --> 01:20:06.560
so Mom and Dad started fasting. Dad

01:20:04.880 --> 01:20:09.920
fasted,

01:20:06.560 --> 01:20:12.960
and they cast those devils out of me.

01:20:09.920 --> 01:20:15.120
And I'm telling you what, I was free.

01:20:12.960 --> 01:20:17.199
And I swore at that moment I'd never go

01:20:15.120 --> 01:20:18.880
back again.

01:20:17.199 --> 01:20:22.080
Never.

01:20:22.080 --> 01:20:26.719
At that point in my life, you have

01:20:24.960 --> 01:20:29.920
people tell you, especially in the Word

01:20:26.719 --> 01:20:32.800
of Faith crowd, 'There ain't no way.'But

01:20:29.920 --> 01:20:35.280
I'm telling you, it was real, and my mom

01:20:32.800 --> 01:20:39.120
and dad can vouch for it. There are

01:20:35.280 --> 01:20:41.440
other people who can vouch for it. My wife saw

01:20:39.120 --> 01:20:43.920
I vomited up a thing that looked like

01:20:41.440 --> 01:20:47.879
oatmeal

01:20:43.920 --> 01:20:47.880
in a towel.

01:20:48.560 --> 01:20:54.080
It stunk like sulfur.

01:20:51.679 --> 01:20:56.239
And Jesus set me free.

01:20:54.080 --> 01:20:59.120
So, I'm telling you, I don't talk about

01:20:56.239 --> 01:21:00.879
things a lot,

01:20:59.120 --> 01:21:02.559
but there's a lot of times I feel like

01:21:00.880 --> 01:21:04.880
there's some things that people should

01:21:02.560 --> 01:21:06.960
know

01:21:04.880 --> 01:21:09.840
because they're walking around

01:21:06.960 --> 01:21:12.960
bound by the devil

01:21:09.840 --> 01:21:14.719
and there's no reason for it.

01:21:12.960 --> 01:21:16.159
You keep going around the mountain,

01:21:14.719 --> 01:21:17.920
around the mountain.

01:21:17.920 --> 01:21:24.000
And you keep running into

01:21:20.560 --> 01:21:26.880
the wall of addictions and things.

01:21:24.000 --> 01:21:31.080
And sometimes you've just got attachments

01:21:26.880 --> 01:21:31.080
and you've just got to get free.

01:21:31.600 --> 01:21:35.040
But the church doesn't want to recognize

01:21:33.040 --> 01:21:36.560
it a lot of times because, you know what,

01:21:35.040 --> 01:21:38.480
they live in compromise and they don't

01:21:36.560 --> 01:21:41.760
believe in the power anyway. They're

01:21:38.480 --> 01:21:43.919
a bunch of weak, limp-wristed Christians.

01:21:41.760 --> 01:21:46.000
And because they live that way and they

01:21:43.920 --> 01:21:48.480
live in compromise,

01:21:46.000 --> 01:21:50.800
they don't want to fast; they don't want

01:21:48.480 --> 01:21:54.799
to seek the Father.

01:21:50.800 --> 01:21:58.000
So they like living in their

01:21:54.800 --> 01:21:59.920
lukewarmness,

01:21:58.000 --> 01:22:02.960
and there's no devil that's challenged

01:21:59.920 --> 01:22:06.639
by your lukewarm limp-wristedness.

01:22:02.960 --> 01:22:10.159
If you have some firepower,

01:22:06.639 --> 01:22:12.639
that's whenever they get upset.

01:22:10.159 --> 01:22:14.879
I've seen it all. When I

01:22:12.639 --> 01:22:17.520
tell you I've had three visitations and

01:22:14.880 --> 01:22:19.920
the devil's come, I really truly am

01:22:17.520 --> 01:22:21.920
telling you he came:

01:22:19.920 --> 01:22:23.840
Satan himself.

01:22:21.920 --> 01:22:26.480
And I've seen him appear before me

01:22:23.840 --> 01:22:30.000
twice.

01:22:26.480 --> 01:22:33.360
He's not shy.

01:22:30.000 --> 01:22:36.679
But I don't give any glory to it.

01:22:33.360 --> 01:22:36.679
He's defeated.

01:22:37.040 --> 01:22:43.360
But all this stuff is not Hollywood;

01:22:40.000 --> 01:22:45.040
it's real. The spirit realm is real, and

01:22:43.360 --> 01:22:49.120
there's a lot of you that play around

01:22:45.040 --> 01:22:50.639
with it. So I just try to help.

01:22:49.120 --> 01:22:52.320
Hopefully that helped some of you a

01:22:50.639 --> 01:22:56.760
little bit. I give you a little bit of

01:22:52.320 --> 01:22:56.759
something, but I don't go into depth.

01:22:57.360 --> 01:23:02.000
I say, 'Lord, I'm

01:23:00.320 --> 01:23:03.360
so tired of being—'I don't want to—

01:23:02.000 --> 01:23:05.760
You know people where you hear that

01:23:03.360 --> 01:23:07.040
'Heaven to gain, hell to shun,'you've got

01:23:05.760 --> 01:23:10.080
all this stuff. And I go, 'It's parroting.

01:23:07.040 --> 01:23:12.400
Just be you.'You

01:23:10.080 --> 01:23:17.719
know, when you

01:23:12.400 --> 01:23:17.719
were so bound—Brandon was so bound.

01:23:18.480 --> 01:23:24.159
I'll never forget it. I was sitting in—and

01:23:21.600 --> 01:23:26.639
then this time opened the

01:23:24.159 --> 01:23:31.679
door again. Obviously,

01:23:26.639 --> 01:23:33.360
I was dealing with a lot of sadness,

01:23:33.360 --> 01:23:36.960
feeling bad for myself, feeling sorry

01:23:35.040 --> 01:23:40.560
for myself all the time. And

01:23:36.960 --> 01:23:42.320
when Megan first got diagnosed with

01:23:40.560 --> 01:23:44.960
autism,

01:23:42.320 --> 01:23:46.880
I was sitting in with Diana and I was

01:23:44.960 --> 01:23:49.760
always thinking, 'I can't keep living

01:23:46.880 --> 01:23:52.960
this way.'And I went to a church service

01:23:49.760 --> 01:23:55.679
in Crescent, Oklahoma, and a man named

01:23:52.960 --> 01:23:58.880
Ronald was there.

01:23:55.679 --> 01:24:02.719
And that spirit of suicide tried to come

01:23:58.880 --> 01:24:05.199
back that I told you about, and he saw it.

01:24:02.719 --> 01:24:07.199
I started groaning

01:24:05.199 --> 01:24:08.719
like a cow on the floor and got rid of

01:24:07.199 --> 01:24:11.519
it, and foam came out of my mouth again,

01:24:08.719 --> 01:24:14.800
and Jesus set me free. But opening

01:24:11.520 --> 01:24:18.080
yourself up for things—I

01:24:14.800 --> 01:24:22.080
was just moments

01:24:18.080 --> 01:24:25.679
away from running my car off a bridge,

01:24:22.080 --> 01:24:28.559
and Jesus set me free.

01:24:25.679 --> 01:24:30.880
Now, if you don't keep yourself in the

01:24:28.560 --> 01:24:32.080
Word of God—and 'faith cometh

01:24:30.880 --> 01:24:34.639
by hearing, and hearing by the word of God'—if

01:24:32.080 --> 01:24:37.440
you don't feed yourself the

01:24:34.639 --> 01:24:40.000
Word and continually get that Word down

01:24:37.440 --> 01:24:42.080
and renew your mind, you open yourself

01:24:40.000 --> 01:24:44.080
up for more stuff to come back, and eight

01:24:42.080 --> 01:24:47.280
more of his buddies will come back. So

01:24:44.080 --> 01:24:49.840
I continually am looking at this Word,

01:24:47.280 --> 01:24:52.239
filling myself up with the word of God,

01:24:49.840 --> 01:24:55.280
listening to Kathryn Kuhlman, reading books,

01:24:52.239 --> 01:24:59.040
filling myself up because I've learned

01:24:55.280 --> 01:25:00.880
don't go back to what you used to be;

01:24:59.040 --> 01:25:02.239
you have to come up higher in

01:25:00.880 --> 01:25:04.880
your relationship and fellowship with

01:25:02.239 --> 01:25:06.799
Him. So you say, 'Well, I don't believe that.'Well,

