01:26:19.840 --> 01:26:24.480
it at the time.

01:26:22.239 --> 01:26:26.400
But you know what? People are fake.

01:26:24.480 --> 01:26:28.320
There's a lot of fake religious

01:26:26.400 --> 01:26:31.519
