01:27:14.719 --> 01:27:20.560
I've been there, and Jesus set me free.

01:27:18.080 --> 01:27:24.000
And if he will do it for me, I know

01:27:20.560 --> 01:27:27.199
he'll do it for you.

01:27:24.000 --> 01:27:30.600
I was bound.

01:27:27.199 --> 01:27:30.599
It was bad

01:27:30.800 --> 01:27:37.745
