01:27:34.000 --> 01:27:41.440
And Jesus set me free.

01:27:37.745 --> 01:27:44.349
So God is so good.

01:27:41.440 --> 01:27:44.349
All right.

01:27:54.480 --> 01:27:58.440
It's all about the blood.

01:27:59.120 --> 01:28:06.360
The spirit realm, y'all, is more real

01:28:02.320 --> 01:28:06.360
than the natural realm.

01:28:06.560 --> 01:28:11.280
When you're able to see people astral

01:28:08.639 --> 01:28:14.159
project and you see the witchcraft and

01:28:11.280 --> 01:28:16.320
you see the things that I see, I don't

01:28:14.159 --> 01:28:19.040
