01:28:20.880 --> 01:28:27.920
angels are so much bigger.

01:28:23.520 --> 01:28:29.600
The angels are so much more powerful.

01:28:27.920 --> 01:28:31.760
Those devils are defeated

01:28:29.600 --> 01:28:34.000
and they always look like pigs. They

01:28:31.760 --> 01:28:36.719
always look like scaly looking things,

01:28:34.000 --> 01:28:39.440
snakes and black figures and all

01:28:36.719 --> 01:28:42.440
kinds of stuff. But the angels are so

01:28:39.440 --> 01:28:42.440
beautiful.

01:28:43.040 --> 01:28:47.120
I'll never forget the three that came

01:28:45.280 --> 01:28:49.440
one night. They were trying to get me

01:28:47.120 --> 01:28:53.159
and they shook my whole house. The whole

01:28:49.440 --> 01:28:53.159
