01:28:53.440 --> 01:28:57.360
And I got up and I thought somebody was

01:28:55.199 --> 01:28:59.440
breaking in.

01:28:57.360 --> 01:29:01.920
And there was one

01:28:59.440 --> 01:29:03.199
that had a pig nose, big red eyes, and they were

01:29:01.920 --> 01:29:05.120
all there. And they

01:29:03.199 --> 01:29:06.159
had scaly skin with hair growing all off

01:29:05.120 --> 01:29:08.080
of them. Looked like somebody out of

01:29:06.159 --> 01:29:11.040
Star Wars.

01:29:08.080 --> 01:29:12.080
And they were grunting and growling.

01:29:11.040 --> 01:29:14.400
But I couldn't figure out how they

01:29:12.080 --> 01:29:16.000
weren't able to get into the house. And

01:29:14.400 --> 01:29:17.360
I was pleading the blood and Dina

01:29:16.000 --> 01:29:21.600
said, 'Somebody's trying to break in.'The

01:29:17.360 --> 01:29:23.519
whole house shook. So I got up and I

01:29:21.600 --> 01:29:26.159
