01:29:30.960 --> 01:29:36.880
and they were wrapped around my whole

01:29:32.239 --> 01:29:39.280
house. These angels were massive.

01:29:36.880 --> 01:29:42.480
They were massive.

01:29:39.280 --> 01:29:45.599
And I was taken back

01:29:42.480 --> 01:29:47.440
by what I saw. But the angels were

01:29:45.600 --> 01:29:49.440
laughing at these demons that were

01:29:47.440 --> 01:29:53.040
trying to get to me. They were laughing.

01:29:49.440 --> 01:29:54.879
But as they laughed, it echoed

01:29:53.040 --> 01:29:59.840
through the neighborhood. I could hear

01:29:54.880 --> 01:30:01.840
it. And it sounded like waters. And

01:29:59.840 --> 01:30:03.760
it was,

01:30:01.840 --> 01:30:05.280
but it wasn't evil. It was

01:30:03.760 --> 01:30:07.199
amazing,

01:30:05.280 --> 01:30:08.639
like echoes. And it echoed

01:30:07.199 --> 01:30:11.759
through the whole thing. You could hear

01:30:08.639 --> 01:30:13.840
it in the neighborhood

01:30:11.760 --> 01:30:18.080
in the spirit.

01:30:13.840 --> 01:30:20.560
And as they—I said, 'Praise God.'And

01:30:18.080 --> 01:30:22.480
those angels knew that I could see them,

01:30:20.560 --> 01:30:24.880
obviously. They turned around and

01:30:22.480 --> 01:30:27.199
looked at me and they went back and they

01:30:24.880 --> 01:30:30.159
went, 'Praise God.'And they started worshipping

01:30:27.199 --> 01:30:33.360
the Lord with me. And I said,

01:30:30.159 --> 01:30:36.080
'Praise God.'And they went,

01:30:33.360 --> 01:30:38.719
'Praise God.'And when they did, it went 'Woo!'and

01:30:36.080 --> 01:30:42.159
the sound was deafening. It

01:30:38.719 --> 01:30:43.679
was so loud. And I could

01:30:42.159 --> 01:30:45.199
see them. And they were looking at the

01:30:43.679 --> 01:30:47.360
Father.

01:30:45.199 --> 01:30:51.440
They were looking at the Father. And I

01:30:47.360 --> 01:30:53.839
got so excited. I go, 'Praise God.'And

01:30:51.440 --> 01:30:56.159
they went, 'Praise God.'And they

01:30:53.840 --> 01:30:58.000
started praising the Lord with me. And

01:30:56.159 --> 01:30:59.440
the moment I started praising the Lord,

01:30:58.000 --> 01:31:01.120
they would praise the Lord. And we would

01:30:59.440 --> 01:31:03.280
echo it back and forth. I don't know how

01:31:01.120 --> 01:31:05.840
long that went on, but I got

01:31:03.280 --> 01:31:08.639
caught up in it because I started, 'Oh,

01:31:05.840 --> 01:31:10.400
praise you, God. You're so good. Oh, Father.'And

01:31:08.639 --> 01:31:12.560
they were worshipping the

01:31:10.400 --> 01:31:14.159
Lord with me.

01:31:12.560 --> 01:31:16.159
I don't even know what happened to the

01:31:14.159 --> 01:31:18.080
demons. They just disappeared. I wasn't

01:31:16.159 --> 01:31:20.638
paying attention to it no more.

01:31:20.639 --> 01:31:25.040
I was just praising the Lord with them because

01:31:22.400 --> 01:31:27.440
I was just in awe at what

01:31:25.040 --> 01:31:29.920
God was allowing me to see because

01:31:27.440 --> 01:31:32.239
at the moment I was scared because I was

01:31:29.920 --> 01:31:34.560
thinking, 'What are these big things outside?'But

01:31:32.239 --> 01:31:37.280
the Lord showed me the

01:31:34.560 --> 01:31:39.199
angels. So, I went to work the next day

01:31:37.280 --> 01:31:41.280
at the church

01:31:39.199 --> 01:31:44.159
and I didn't know that I had

01:31:41.280 --> 01:31:45.519
glory on me because the pastor said—I

01:31:44.159 --> 01:31:47.120
told him when I saw him—he said, 'Brenton, I

01:31:45.520 --> 01:31:51.199
believe it. There's actually a light.

01:31:47.120 --> 01:31:54.199
There's a glow on you.'And I thought,

01:31:51.199 --> 01:31:54.199
'Wow,

01:31:55.040 --> 01:32:02.400
the glory is transferable

01:31:59.120 --> 01:32:04.080
like cross-pollination

01:32:02.400 --> 01:32:05.360
when you get over in that realm of the

01:32:04.080 --> 01:32:08.880
spirit.'It

01:32:05.360 --> 01:32:10.880
gets on you. It changes you from the

01:32:08.880 --> 01:32:12.960
inside out.

01:32:10.880 --> 01:32:16.239
