01:32:16.239 --> 01:32:20.159
And I'll never forget those angels

01:32:18.400 --> 01:32:22.320
and how all the time the Lord showed me

01:32:20.159 --> 01:32:24.080
things like that like he did here.

01:32:22.320 --> 01:32:28.159
And the angels stood there and I've

01:32:24.080 --> 01:32:30.400
seen them and I saw the opal suit angel

01:32:28.159 --> 01:32:32.400
and they all look

01:32:30.400 --> 01:32:34.719
different. But I'm going to tell you,

01:32:32.400 --> 01:32:36.960
we don't get stuck on that.

01:32:34.719 --> 01:32:39.840
But I'm going to tell you that

01:32:36.960 --> 01:32:43.159
the spirit realm is more real than

01:32:39.840 --> 01:32:43.159
the natural.

01:32:43.760 --> 01:32:49.360
You're one breath away. To be absent

01:32:46.960 --> 01:32:51.520
from the body is to be present with the

01:32:49.360 --> 01:32:54.639
