01:32:51.520 --> 01:32:56.560
way. The moment you take your last

01:32:54.639 --> 01:33:00.064
breath,

01:33:00.080 --> 01:33:03.320
you're done.

01:33:04.480 --> 01:33:10.320
That moment, you're either on your way

01:33:07.360 --> 01:33:13.280
there or there. It's that

01:33:10.320 --> 01:33:15.519
fast. But the spirit realm's that real.

01:33:13.280 --> 01:33:17.599
But most people never know that

01:33:15.520 --> 01:33:20.239
until they take their last breath. And

01:33:17.600 --> 01:33:22.480
they didn't even realize

01:33:20.239 --> 01:33:24.638
that. Like they say, there's a heaven to

01:33:22.480 --> 01:33:26.879
gain and a hell to shun. Which side are

01:33:24.639 --> 01:33:29.360
you on?

01:33:26.880 --> 01:33:32.719
And I've seen the other side. I've seen

01:33:29.360 --> 01:33:35.199
Satan's palace.

01:33:32.719 --> 01:33:37.199
It's onyx with blood flowing

01:33:35.199 --> 01:33:39.759
from his altar.

01:33:37.199 --> 01:33:41.839
I don't know how he did it. I've seen

01:33:39.760 --> 01:33:43.440
the principalities that surround

01:33:41.840 --> 01:33:45.440
him.

01:33:43.440 --> 01:33:46.799
I've seen the steps. I've seen it as he

01:33:45.440 --> 01:33:51.120
took me in there and offered me

01:33:46.800 --> 01:33:54.880
everything. I've seen it all.

01:33:51.120 --> 01:33:56.639
Satan's palace is all black onyx.

01:33:54.880 --> 01:34:00.560
It's the most demonic thing I've ever

01:33:56.639 --> 01:34:03.960
seen in my life where he sits. And it's

01:34:00.560 --> 01:34:03.960
not in hell.

01:34:04.080 --> 01:34:09.040
It's not in hell.

01:34:06.639 --> 01:34:12.320
It's right above us.

01:34:09.040 --> 01:34:15.040
It's not in hell. His throne room is not

01:34:12.320 --> 01:34:16.719
in hell. It's right above; it's

01:34:15.040 --> 01:34:18.239
up here.

01:34:16.719 --> 01:34:19.760
And then there's another realm

01:34:18.239 --> 01:34:22.000
when you push through that and it's the

01:34:19.760 --> 01:34:24.400
glory realm. But I'm

01:34:22.000 --> 01:34:27.199
telling you, heaven is in a dimension of

01:34:24.400 --> 01:34:29.599
itself. It's the most beautiful place you've

01:34:27.199 --> 01:34:32.719
ever seen in your life.

01:34:29.600 --> 01:34:35.760
I've been allowed to go and see it. How

01:34:32.719 --> 01:34:38.880
many times now you think, son?

01:34:35.760 --> 01:34:41.920
Several. It's a lot. But I always come

01:34:38.880 --> 01:34:43.760
back and I tell everybody what I see.

01:34:41.920 --> 01:34:45.120
My mom brought it up to me the other

01:34:43.760 --> 01:34:47.440
day. She goes, 'You remember whenever

01:34:45.120 --> 01:34:49.840
Debbie's daughter died in the van

01:34:47.440 --> 01:34:51.440
accident?'She

01:34:49.840 --> 01:34:53.520
said, 'You saw her and she was

01:34:51.440 --> 01:34:56.000
looking and she was—she looked back and

01:34:53.520 --> 01:34:57.760
she was looking at her body when she got

01:34:56.000 --> 01:35:01.520
in a tragic car accident.'I

01:34:57.760 --> 01:35:03.120
said, 'Yeah, I remember her

01:35:01.520 --> 01:35:07.719
standing in the flowers and she was

01:35:03.120 --> 01:35:07.719
puzzled because she went home early.'And

01:35:08.000 --> 01:35:11.920
I remember her standing there and

01:35:09.760 --> 01:35:14.080
looking at the flowers and the

01:35:11.920 --> 01:35:15.840
flowers didn't die as she was standing

01:35:14.080 --> 01:35:17.920
in the flowers. They weren't crushed by

01:35:15.840 --> 01:35:19.679
her weight. She walked in the midst of

01:35:17.920 --> 01:35:22.320
these flowers, but they were colors that

01:35:19.679 --> 01:35:24.239
I've never seen before.

01:35:22.320 --> 01:35:26.639
Shades,

01:35:24.239 --> 01:35:28.480
shades of beautiful colors.

01:35:28.480 --> 01:35:33.280
And she looked back at her body and she

01:35:31.520 --> 01:35:37.040
looked, and Jesus grabbed a hold of her

01:35:33.280 --> 01:35:38.320
hand and he took her in.

01:35:37.040 --> 01:35:42.159
People were like, 'Why didn't she come

01:35:38.320 --> 01:35:44.880
back? She was like 11 years old.'That

01:35:42.159 --> 01:35:47.679
was a while ago, but I'll never

01:35:44.880 --> 01:35:50.800
forget the Lord allowed me to see that

01:35:47.679 --> 01:35:52.960
whenever she left her body and I saw her

01:35:50.800 --> 01:35:55.360
