01:35:52.960 --> 01:35:57.280
looking back. There are

01:35:55.360 --> 01:36:01.759
so many things that I've

01:35:57.280 --> 01:36:03.360
been able to—I don't know

01:36:01.760 --> 01:36:06.320
why the Lord allows me to see this

01:36:03.360 --> 01:36:08.799
stuff. I don't know. But I see a lot of

01:36:06.320 --> 01:36:10.960
stuff. And the Lord allowed me to see

01:36:08.800 --> 01:36:14.239
people die. I see things come back to

01:36:10.960 --> 01:36:16.639
life. I've seen, like I said,

01:36:14.239 --> 01:36:20.559
the spirit realm is more real than

01:36:16.639 --> 01:36:24.480
even the air that you breathe.

01:36:20.560 --> 01:36:28.080
The demonic show off all the time. I see

01:36:24.480 --> 01:36:30.159
it a lot, but I never talk about it.

01:36:28.080 --> 01:36:32.320
I don't give them praise. I don't

01:36:30.159 --> 01:36:34.879
give them glory because I could always

01:36:32.320 --> 01:36:37.519
see them inside

01:36:34.880 --> 01:36:40.080
of people. And the moment you

01:36:37.520 --> 01:36:43.400
acknowledge them, they get strength

01:36:40.080 --> 01:36:43.400
from pride.

01:36:46.239 --> 01:36:51.919
The more

01:36:49.360 --> 01:36:53.839
you fear them, you reverence that more

01:36:51.920 --> 01:36:56.400
than you fear God.

01:36:53.840 --> 01:36:58.400
They get strength,

01:36:56.400 --> 01:37:00.879
and I've seen them; they draw from that

01:36:58.400 --> 01:37:04.080
energy of fear. Fear tolerated is

01:37:00.880 --> 01:37:08.760
faith contaminated. It is true.

01:37:04.080 --> 01:37:08.760
But they get strength from fear,

01:37:10.960 --> 01:37:15.400
and it's harder to get them out.

01:37:17.199 --> 01:37:22.159
It's interesting

01:37:19.440 --> 01:37:26.480
when you fear, but when you fear Him and

01:37:22.159 --> 01:37:29.599
reverence Him, they're weak.

01:37:26.480 --> 01:37:31.280
But Satan is the same way.

01:37:29.600 --> 01:37:33.600
And I've seen him present things to

01:37:31.280 --> 01:37:35.280
people. I see him going to meetings. He

01:37:33.600 --> 01:37:38.719
talks to a lot of people with a lot of

01:37:35.280 --> 01:37:40.719
money. It's his wheelhouse. But he

01:37:38.719 --> 01:37:44.560
always has meetings with these huge

01:37:40.719 --> 01:37:47.600
business people like George and Bill.

01:37:44.560 --> 01:37:49.040
They're friends with him.

01:37:47.600 --> 01:37:52.320
I always wondered about the man in

01:37:49.040 --> 01:37:54.080
China, too. He always talks to him,

01:37:52.320 --> 01:37:55.440
but the Lord allowed me to look

01:37:54.080 --> 01:37:58.840
at him, and I watch and I'm able to

01:37:55.440 --> 01:37:58.839
hear their meetings.

01:37:59.040 --> 01:38:02.360
It's interesting.

01:38:03.440 --> 01:38:06.440
But

01:38:17.520 --> 01:38:22.159
I could actually sit here and

01:38:19.440 --> 01:38:23.440
talk to you all night about it.

01:38:22.159 --> 01:38:25.440
There's a lot of things I could tell

01:38:23.440 --> 01:38:29.440
you,

01:38:25.440 --> 01:38:31.280
but I just give bits and pieces because

01:38:29.440 --> 01:38:35.320
a lot of you don't believe it. And

01:38:31.280 --> 01:38:35.320
I'm not going to cast my pearls,

01:38:36.960 --> 01:38:42.040
but there's things that I see that

